reviewText: The title and description makes it sound like this is an hour long movie about Chipmunks & Batman. This movie was really 3 little 15-20 min cartoons put together. They were Batman, Treasure Island, and Sherlock Holmes. It's still cute - because we like the Chipmunks; however, I wouldn't have purchased it had I known it was not an entire movie on Batman.
summary: MISLEADING TITLE - Not a Batman movie

reviewText: OK, Let's stop the repeats. I've been frustrated with the Munks releases. Several of them don't even have title cards like they aired on TV. It's getting to be that all of the episodes are repeats on a disc. Since I already own this episode, I won't be getting this release. The second Valentines release, Driving Dave Crazy are all repeat episodes. NO THANKS. I'm saving my money.
